\id TDX Topical Index for the Anjam NT Robert Rucker 13-September-2000 
\h Anjam Mutu Qudei 
\toc1 Anjam Mutu Qudei 
\toc2 Anjam Mutu Qudei 
\mt1 Anjam Mutu Qudei  
\p Ni qalie bei oqajqa are soqnimqa kiyo gulbe bei inoq di brantimqa kiyo ni Qotei aqa anjam mutu endi sisiy.  
\li1 Ni Qotei qa qalieqajqa marsimqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Aposel 14:14-17; Aposel 17:22-31; Rom 1:18-23; Rom 11:33-36; 1 Korin 8:4-6; Mak 12:29-30; Jon 4:23-24; 1 Timoti 1:17; 1 Timoti 6:15-16; Hibru 4:13; Hibru 10:30-31; Jems 1:17; 1 Pita 1:14-17; 1 Jon 1:5; 1 Jon 4:7-12, 16; 2 Korin 1:3; Jut 24-25; Uli Anjam 4:8-11; Uli Anjam 15:3-4\xt*  
\li1 Ni Qotei aqa Ŋiri Yesus Kristus qa qalieqajqa marsimqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Jon 1:1-18; Filipai 2:5-11; Kolosi 1:15-20; Kolosi 2:9-10; Hibru 1:1-14; Rom 1:3-4; 2 Korin 4:4-6; Luk 1:26-38; Galesia 4:4-5; Matyu 16:13-17; Jon 5:19-29; Jon 6:35-40; Jon 11:25-27; Jon 14:5-11; Jon 17:1-5; Jon 20:26-31; Aposel 3:13-16; Aposel 4:10-12; 1 Jon 2:1-2; 1 Jon 5:20; Uli Anjam 19:11-16\xt*  
\li1 Ni are qalonum kiyo, “Qotei a e qa are qalosaieqnu.” Degamqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt 1 Jon 4:9-10; Rom 5:8; Jon 3:16; 1 Timoti 2:3-6; 2 Pita 3:9\xt*  
\li1 Ni are qalonum kiyo, “E une saiqoji.” Degamqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Rom 3:10-12, 23-24; Rom 5:12; Galesia 3:22; 1 Jon 1:8-10; Jon 3:18-20, 36; Aposel 17:30-31; Kolosi 3:5-10; Rom 6:23; Galesia 6:7-8; 2 Tesalonaika 1:7-9; 1 Pita 4:3-5; Uli Anjam 20:11-15\xt*  
\li1 Ni are qalonum kiyo, “Qotei na ijo une kobotqasai.” Degamqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Aposel 5:31; Aposel 10:43; Aposel 26:18; Efesus 1:7; Kolosi 1:13-14; Kolosi 2:13-14; 1 Timoti 1:15-16; Hibru 10:17-18; 1 Jon 1:8-10\xt*  
\li1 Ino areqalo qujai agi Yesus Kristus na ni oqajqa. Deqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Jon 1:12; Jon 3:15-18, 36; Jon 14:6; Jon 20:31; Aposel 4:12; Aposel 16:30-31; Rom 3:20-22; Rom 10:9-10; Galesia 2:16; Efesus 2:8-9\xt*  
\li1 Ni qaliesai, ni ŋambile gaigai sqam kiyo sai kiyo? Deqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Jon 3:1-16; Jon 5:19-29; Jon 11:25-26; Jon 14:6; Jon 17:2-3; Jon 20:31; Rom 8:10-17; 2 Korin 5:17; Efesus 2:1-6; Kolosi 2:13; Taitus 3:4-7; 1 Jon 5:11-13\xt*  
\li1 Ni maronum kiyo, “E Qotei pailyoqnqai e?” Degamqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Matyu 6:5-13; Matyu 7:7-11; Matyu 14:23; Matyu 18:19-20; Mak 1:35; Mak 11:24-25; Luk 5:16; Luk 6:12; Luk 18:1-8; Luk 21:36; Jon 14:13-14; Jon 15:7; Jon 16:23-24; Rom 8:26-27; Rom 12:12; Efesus 6:18; Filipai 4:6-7; Kolosi 4:2; 1 Tesalonaika 5:17; 1 Timoti 2:1-4, 8; 1 Timoti 4:4-5; Hibru 4:16; Hibru 10:19-22; Jems 1:5-8; Jems 4:2-3; Jems 5:13-18; 1 Pita 4:7; 1 Jon 3:21-22; 1 Jon 5:14-15\xt*  
\li1 Ni maronum kiyo, “E iŋgi kiye qa Qotei pailyqai?” Degamqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Luk 11:1-4; Luk 22:32, 39-46; Jon 17:1-26; Aposel 4:24-31; Aposel 16:25; Rom 1:9-10; Rom 10:1-2; Rom 15:30-33; 2 Korin 12:7-10; Efesus 1:15-20; Efesus 3:14-21; Efesus 6:19-20; Filipai 1:3-5, 9-11; Kolosi 1:9-12; Kolosi 4:3-4; 1 Tesalonaika 3:9-13; 2 Tesalonaika 1:11-12; 2 Tesalonaika 3:1-2; Hibru 5:7; Hibru 7:25\xt*  
\li1 Ni gulbe ti jaqatiŋ ti eqnum kiyo. Degamqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Rom 8:18-25, 28, 35-37; Rom 12:12; 2 Korin 1:3-5; 2 Korin 4:16-18; Jems 1:2-4; 1 Pita 1:3-9; 1 Pita 2:19-23; 1 Pita 5:8-10\xt*  
\li1 Ni maimimqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Matyu 4:23-25; Matyu 9:35; Matyu 11:2-5; Aposel 3:1-6; Aposel 8:4-8; Aposel 19:11-16; Aposel 28:8-9; 1 Korin 12:9, 29-30; 2 Korin 12:7-10; 1 Timoti 5:23; 2 Timoti 4:20; Jems 5:14-15\xt*  
\li1 Ni moiqajqa ulaosimqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Jon 6:39-40; Jon 11:17-27; Jon 14:1-4; Rom 8:38-39; Rom 14:7-9; 1 Korin 15:12-58; 2 Korin 5:1-10; Filipai 1:20-24; 1 Tesalonaika 4:13-18; Hibru 2:14-15; Uli Anjam 14:13; Uli Anjam 21:1-4; Uli Anjam 22:1-5\xt*  
\li1 Ni qalieqajqa, Kristen naŋgi kumbra kiye dauryqab? Deqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Jon 13:34-35; Rom 12:9-13; Galesia 5:22-26; Efesus 4:25-32; Kolosi 3:12-17; 1 Tesalonaika 5:12-22; Taitus 2:11-14; Jems 3:13-18; 2 Pita 1:3-9\xt*  
\li1 Ni qalieqajqa, kumbra bei a uge kiyo bole kiyo? Deqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Rom 1:18-32; 1 Korin 6:9-11; Galesia 5:19-21; Efesus 5:3-5; Kolosi 3:5-10; Jems 4:17; 1 Pita 4:3; 1 Jon 2:15-17; 1 Jon 3:4-5\xt*  
\li1 Ni are qalonum kiyo, “E Qotei aqa kumbra dauryqa keresai.” Degamqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Jon 14:16-23; 1 Korin 10:13; Efesus 3:20-21; Filipai 1:6; Filipai 4:13; Kolosi 1:11-12; 1 Tesalonaika 5:23-24; Hibru 13:5-6; 1 Jon 5:3-5\xt*  
\li1 Ni Kristen unum deqa tamo qudei na ni ugeugeimeqnub. Deqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Matyu 5:10-12; Mak 13:9-13; Luk 12:4-9; Jon 15:18-21; Jon 16:1-4; Aposel 5:41; Rom 8:35-37; Rom 12:14, 17-21; 1 Korin 4:11-13; 2 Korin 4:8-12; 2 Korin 12:10; Filipai 1:28-29; 2 Tesalonaika 1:4-8; 2 Timoti 3:10-13; Hibru 10:32-39; Hibru 12:3-4; 1 Pita 3:13-17; 1 Pita 4:12-19; Uli Anjam 2:10\xt*  
\li1 Ni are qalonum kiyo, “E Kristen tamo qudei naŋgi ti korooqnqasai.” Degamqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Matyu 18:19-20; Aposel 2:41-47; Rom 12:4-8; Efesus 1:22-23; Efesus 4:11-16; Kolosi 3:15-17; 1 Timoti 4:13; Hibru 10:24-25\xt*  
\li1 Tamo bei na ni kumbra uge emimqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Matyu 6:12-15; Matyu 18:21-35; Mak 11:25; Luk 17:3-4; Rom 12:17-21; Efesus 4:31-32; Kolosi 3:13\xt*  
\li1 Ni tamo ti uŋa ti unum kiyo? Degamqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt 1 Korin 7:1-16; Efesus 5:21-33; Kolosi 3:18-19; Taitus 2:3-5; Hibru 13:4; 1 Pita 3:1-7; Matyu 5:31-32; Matyu 19:3-9; Luk 16:18; Rom 7:2-3\xt*  
\li1 Ni uŋa bei kiyo tamo bei kiyo ombla ŋeiqajqa are soqnimqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Matyu 5:27-28; Jon 8:2-11; Rom 13:8-10; 1 Korin 6:9-20; Galesia 5:19; Efesus 5:3; Kolosi 3:5-6; 1 Tesalonaika 4:1-8; Hibru 13:4; Jut 7\xt*  
\li1 Ni aŋgro ti sosimqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Efesus 6:1-4; Kolosi 3:20-21; 1 Timoti 3:4-5\xt*  
\li1 Ino ai abu naŋgi soqnibqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Matyu 15:3-6; Efesus 6:1-3; Kolosi 3:20; 1 Timoti 5:4-8\xt*  
\li1 Ino was bei a gulbe ti soqnimqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Matyu 7:12; Matyu 25:31-46; Luk 3:10-11; Luk 6:38; Aposel 11:27-30; 1 Korin 10:24; 2 Korin 8:1-15; 2 Korin 9:1-15; Galesia 6:9-10; Filipai 4:14-19; Hibru 10:24; Hibru 13:1-3, 16; Jems 1:27; Jems 2:15-16; 1 Jon 3:16-18\xt*  
\li1 Ni une bei atqajqa are prugmimqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Matyu 6:13; Matyu 26:41; 1 Korin 10:13; Hibru 2:18; Hibru 4:14-16; Jems 1:12-15\xt*  
\li1 Ni une bei atonum kiyo? Degamqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Luk 15:11-24; Rom 6:1-23; 1 Jon 1:9–2:2; Jems 4:7-10; Uli Anjam 3:19-20; Hibru 12:1-2\xt*  
\li1 Ni Satan aqa mondor uge naŋgi qa ti ulaoqnsimqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Matyu 4:1-11; Matyu 6:13; Luk 22:31-32; Jon 17:14-19; Rom 16:19-20; 1 Korin 16:13; 2 Korin 12:7-10; Efesus 3:20-21; Efesus 6:10-18; 1 Tesalonaika 3:5-8; 2 Tesalonaika 3:3; Jems 4:7-8; 1 Pita 5:8-11; 1 Jon 4:4; Uli Anjam 12:7-12\xt*  
\li1 Ni tamo bei qa minjiŋ oqimqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Galesia 5:22-23; Efesus 4:26; Kolosi 3:8, 13; Jems 1:19-20\xt*  
\li1 Ni diqoqnsim ino segi ñam soqtoqnsimqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Matyu 5:3-12; Matyu 18:1-5; Luk 14:7-11; Luk 18:9-14; Rom 12:16; 1 Korin 4:7; 2 Korin 10:17-18; Efesus 4:2; Kolosi 3:12-13; Jems 4:6, 13-16; 1 Pita 5:5-7\xt*  
\li1 Ni yumal anjam mareqnum kiyo? Degamqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Efesus 4:29; Efesus 5:4; Filipai 4:8; Kolosi 3:8; 1 Timoti 4:12; Jems 1:26; Jems 3:9-10\xt*  
\li1 Ni gisaŋ anjam bei marqajqa are prugmimqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Efesus 4:25; Kolosi 3:9; 1 Pita 3:10; Jon 8:44; Uli Anjam 21:8; Uli Anjam 22:15\xt*  
\li1 Tamo qudei na ni osib naŋgi koba na ya uge uysib nanariqajqa mermibqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Rom 13:13; 1 Korin 5:9-11; 1 Korin 6:9-10; Galesia 5:19-21; Efesus 5:18; 1 Timoti 3:1-3; Taitus 1:7; 1 Pita 4:3-5\xt*  
\li1 Ni iŋgi iŋgi koba oqnqajqa are prugmeqnu kiyo? Degamqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Matyu 6:19-21, 24-34; Luk 12:13-21, 32-34; Aposel 20:35; 1 Timoti 6:6-10, 17-19; Hibru 13:5-6\xt*  
\li1 Tamo qudei na ni gisaŋ qotei naŋgi qa louqajqa mermibqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Matyu 4:10; Aposel 17:22-31; 1 Korin 5:11; 1 Korin 6:9-11; 1 Korin 8:1-13; 1 Korin 10:1-22; 2 Korin 6:14-18; Galesia 5:19-21; 1 Tesalonaika 1:9-10; 1 Jon 5:21; Uli Anjam 21:8; Uli Anjam 22:15\xt*  
\li1 Ni qalieqajqa, “E kumbra kiye ijo gate kokba naŋgi enjrqai?” Deqa ni anjam mutu endi sisiy:  
\mi \xt Matyu 22:15-22; Rom 13:1-7; 1 Timoti 2:1-4; Taitus 3:1; Hibru 13:17; 1 Pita 2:13-17\xt*  